{
  "page": "Three Jeynes",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Three Jeynes: Jeyne Smallwood, Jeyne Mooton, and Jeyne Merryweather by coldraindropsss ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>three Jeynes</b> was the nickname used by <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> to refer to <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Merryweather\" title=\"Jeyne Merryweather\">Jeyne Merryweather</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Mooton\" title=\"Jeyne Mooton\">Jeyne Mooton</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Smallwood\" title=\"Jeyne Smallwood\">Jeyne Smallwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Three_Jeynes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The three Jeynes were among the many <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidens</a> who suffered what was called the \"<a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_curse\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day curse\">Maiden's Day curse</a>\" prior to the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>. Rumors spread saying they liked to dress in <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>'s garb, visit <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">brothels</a> along the <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Silk\" title=\"Street of Silk\">Street of Silk</a> and kiss and fondle women as if they were boys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Three_Jeynes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215938\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.044 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 918/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 518/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1157/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   36.616      1 -total\n 75.84%   27.769      1 Template:Date\n 19.14%    7.007      2 Template:Ref\n 12.94%    4.737      2 Template:Ref/core\n  4.29%    1.570      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:27357-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404215938 and revision id 334358\n -->\n",
